<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>上传工资表</title>
    #parse("comm/head.vm")
    <link href="#springUrl('/resource/css/plugins/webuploader/webuploader.css')" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="#springUrl('/resource/js/plugins/webuploader/webuploader.nolog.min.js')"></script>
    <script src="#springUrl('/resource/js/salary/rapidlyPayrollExcel.js')"></script>
    <style>
        body, html {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .upAll {
            height: 100%;
            width: 95%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .upTop {
            height: 28px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 28px;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .upTop1 {
            width: 50%;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            float: left;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-radius: 3px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .upTop1 img, .upTop2 img {
            margin-top: 3px;
        }

        .upTop2 {
            width: 50%;
            border: 1px solid #999;
            float: left;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-left: none;
            border-radius: 0 3px 3px;
            color: #999;
            cursor: pointer;
            background: #ddd;
        }

        .upBatch {
            height: 30px;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .upFile {
            width: 117px;
            height: 30px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            margin: auto;
            z-index: 3;
            opacity: 0;
            cursor: pointer
        }

        .upText {
            width: 117px;
            height: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 30px;
            background: #1394ff;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 3px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .upAskFor {
            width: 100%;
            height: 178px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            position: relative
        }

        .upAsk {
            width: 520px;
            height: 178px;
            border: 1px dashed #999;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .upAsk p {
            line-height: 35px;
            padding-left: 30px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .upAskP1 {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-weight: 600
        }

        .upAsk p span {
            text-decoration: underline;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #1394ff;
        }

        table {
            width: 595px;
            height: 150px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px auto 0;
        }

        table tr td {
            border: 1px solid #b8dae5;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .preTan {
            display: none;
            width: 600px;
            height: 110px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: #ddd 2px 3px 30px 20px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 21%;
            right: 0;
            margin: auto;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .preTan p {
            padding-top: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .preTan p span {
            color: #1394ff;
        }

        .progress {
            width: 90%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="upAll">
    <div class="upTop">
        <div class="upTop1"><img src="#springUrl('/resource/img/salary/2.2up1.png')" alt="">&nbsp;上传工资表</div>
        <div class="upTop2"><img src="#springUrl('/resource/img/salary/2.2up2.png')" alt="">&nbsp;预览并发工资</div>
    </div>
    <div id="picker">批量上传</div>
    <div class="upAskFor">
        <div class="upAsk">
            <p class="upAskP1">上传要求</p>
            <p>1、支持WPS、excel2003以上版本文件。</p>
            <p>2、按照模板格式录入正确的信息。</p>
            <p>3、支持格式见示例 <span><a href="$!{BatchRapidlyTemplate}">下载模板文件</a></span></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <table class="upFooter">
        <tr>
            <td colspan='5'>示例</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>姓名</td>
            <td>身份证号</td>
            <td>工资卡开户行</td>
            <td>工资卡卡号</td>
            <td>实发金额（元）</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>汪洋</td>
            <td>111111111111111111</td>
            <td>工商银行</td>
            <td>111111111111111111</td>
            <td>5000</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <div class="preTan">
        <p>批量上传 <span></span><span id="uploadProgres">0%</span></p>
        <div>
            <!--用来存放文件信息-->
            <div id="thelist" class="uploader-list">
            ##                    <p class="state">上传中</p>
                <div class="progress progress-striped active">
                    <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 14%;"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>